               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit and explicit of Text I; name of the King; titles of the books to be read; initial word of the prayers to be read; numbers of the prayers; directives to the ministers and their abbreviations; words ʾǝgäle and ʾǝgälit; elements of Ethiopic numerals; elements of the punctuation signs; doxology on fol. 19v. &#xD;
On the incipit page of Text I (fol.5r), a few lines are rubricated, alternating with black lines.</rubric>
